msgid "MM_addonSummary2_text"
msgstr "• 4 new scenarios\n• 8 new investigators\n• 364 new cards"

msgid "MM_addonDescription2_text"
msgstr "Under Dark Waves is an expansion to Arkham Horror that takes the investigators beyond Arkham's city limits to research strange happenings in the coastal towns of Innsmouth and Kingsport. They face new threats and are joined by new investigators, bolstered with additional tools and allies to help them overcome the ever-escalating plots that threaten their world."
"\n• 4 scenarios"
								"\n• 8 investigators"
								"\n• 4 new neighborhoods"
								"\n• 8 travel route tiles"
								"\n• 2 Mystery tiles"
								"\n• 4 headline cards"
								"\n• 60 archive cards"
								"\n• 12 anomaly cards"
								"\n• 24 terror cards"
								"\n• 104 event cards"
								"\n• 72 encounter cards"
								"\n• 2 ally cards"
								"\n• 4 item cards"
								"\n• 2 spell cards"
								"\n• 14 special cards"
								"\n• 25 starting cards"
								"\n• 8 condition cards"
								"\n• 21 monster cards" 

msgid "MM_addonSummary3_text"
msgstr "• 3 new scenarios\n• 4 new investigators\n• 260 new cards"

msgid "MM_addonDescription3_text"
msgstr "Secrets of the Order is an expansion to Arkham Horror that brings the investigation back to the classic neighborhood of French Hill and beyond our reality to the terrifying Underworld. As one of Arkham's oldest areas, French Hill is home to ancient secrets, potential allies, and mysterious threats. Meanwhile, in the deepest layer of the Dreamlands, beyond the veil of the waking world, the Underworld is a realm of monsters and madness, where only the very desperate dare to roam."
"\n• 3 scenarios"
								"\n• 4 investigators"
								"\n• 2 new neighborhoods"
								"\n• 2 threshold tiles"
								"\n• 2 Mystery tiles"
								"\n• 4 headline cards"
								"\n• 45 archive cards"
								"\n• 12 anomaly cards"
								"\n• 80 event cards"
								"\n• 54 encounter cards"
								"\n• 3 ally cards"
								"\n• 3 item cards"
								"\n• 2 spell cards"
								"\n• 18 special cards"
								"\n• 12 starting cards"
								"\n• 6 condition cards"
								"\n• 20 monster cards" 

msgid "MM_addonSummary4_text"
msgstr "• 4 variations for base investigators"

